# Internationalization (i18n)

This application supports multiple languages through a comprehensive i18n system:

## Core i18n Structure

- [src/i18n](mdc:src/i18n) - Contains i18n configuration, translations, and helpers
- [src/app/[lang]](mdc:src/app/[lang]) - Dynamic routes based on language parameter
- [src/app/_dictionaries](mdc:src/app/_dictionaries) - Dictionary files for different languages

## Implementation

- The application uses Next.js route parameters to handle language selection
- The `[lang]` directory creates dynamic routes that include language code
- Dictionary files provide translations for different parts of the application

